&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;ARIEL, Wash. (October 16, 2025) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family:lato,lato_embeddedfont,lato_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&mdash; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Despite recent rainfall across the Pacific Northwest, dry conditions continue to impact Pacific Power&rsquo;s reservoirs on the Lewis River, resulting in a boat ramp closure this weekend.&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

