&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;Beginning November 1, these fees will help cover increased operating and maintenance costs at some of our recreation facilities. Thousands of guests enjoy the parks and campgrounds every year, and this change will allow Pacific Power to continue providing exceptional experiences for visitors&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(136, 23, 152)"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt; while keeping prices reasonable.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
